item.title: Proxy client?
item.dc:creator: @blacknight blacknight
item.description:
@blacknight wrote:

java -DsocksProxyHost=12.345.678.910 -DsocksProxyPort=1234 -noverify -Xmx500m -cp .;./OUTPUT;./OUTPUT/unrenamed.jar;./BotClasses; Bot

12.345.678.910 replace with the proxy
Botclasses change to the folder that has all that .java .class files in it.

so after it should look like this.

@echo off
java -noverify -Xmx500m -cp .;./OUTPUT;./OUTPUT/unrenamed.jar;./BotClasses;./LIB; Bot %1
pause
